    author: "Saleem Raja",
    excerpt: "Key Takeaways • AI virtual agents leverage LLMs and machine learning for advanced customer interactions • 78% of enterprises report cost savings of 25-45% after implementing AI agents • Implementation requires careful planning and typically takes 3-6 months • ROI statistics show 300% average return ",
